summary:
I am a nutrition researcher who is passionate about investigating nutrition related problems that can help improve the livelihoods and nutrition status of the vulnerable members of societies.

Key words: nutrition, nutrition interventions, micronutrients, quantitative research, vitamin A, zinc, deficiency, compartmental modelling
